  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Defects should be identified and removed as early as possible&amp;nbsp;in the lifecycle when they are least costly to fix.&#xD;
    Effective detection practices and tools&amp;nbsp;will prevent software from shipping with a large number of defects.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Symptoms that indicate the need to increase defect detection include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        High post-shipment or customer-reported defects&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        High rate of fixes which have to be reworked&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Projects lack quality objectives&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Projects lack test plans and related metrics&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Compressed test cycles due to late code availability or schedule slips.&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solutions&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following solutions help to&amp;nbsp;increase defect detection:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_build_process_9E509595.html&quot; guid=&quot;_eOf00LRZEd6qwtTa3nKvcw&quot;>Improve Build Process&lt;/a> - Increase Build and Test automation to reduce manual and&#xD;
        insufficient build and test procedures.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_performance_testing_82D8523D.html&quot; guid=&quot;_2WqiwMyDEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Improve Performance Testing&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Verify the system meets its performance&#xD;
        requirements&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_security_testing_E029D22E.html&quot; guid=&quot;_5rJyUMyDEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Improve Security Testing&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Verify the system meets its security&#xD;
        requirements&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_test_effectiveness_F97F58E1.html&quot; guid=&quot;_xwg3AMyDEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Improve Test Effectiveness&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Improve the effectiveness of testing&#xD;
        activities by improving test procedures and increasing the percentage of automated tests.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:ContentDescription>
